Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭開了阿良良木月火的真正身份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的故事也將畫上終止符了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把我和火憐醬當小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那個有點小聰明有有點煩人的年紀小的妹妹的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和我所愛的夥伴們的故事終於完結了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白金火大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿良良木月火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炎姐妹中的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀小的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學二年級
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月出生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14歲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B型血
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點狂躁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你說我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點小聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以對火憐醬發火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要對我發火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格有雙面性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是不死身的偽物的故事
